{"tid":1627663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日集中要人數推爆港島！！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T16:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T19:03:20.000Z","uid":226991,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f8314828c48badfd2593ee2e8bc717a025cfad1e","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"講左兩日，今日已經好多和理非，銀髮出左黎呼籲聽日2點維園。唔好再玩佢地啦唔該。依家硬推九龍，根本只會得連登仔去，大部分和理非已經準備好聽日維園<br />\n<br />\n點解係要咁急推九龍，已經好耐冇一次吹大雞。<br />\n和理非，勇武再次818咁 。<br />\n依家民怨沸騰，係時候比政府知一次，民意依然係我地到<br />\n我地要既係二百萬以上既人數。<br />\n唔好分散人頭啦唔該。<br />\n<br />\n聽日和理非一日，無反應，後日幫政府賀重陽分區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de90aae403609326c4301c579f772475c3c6496","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"d43f46529e831a7897a5b61586bfdb0906052957","tid":1627663,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mexyDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mexyDa.png&h=365657f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbea842e7a8a9f5f2e61ef7ec18aee50e9720dc5","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"52182ee232be300ad11e63104a22369750dd56cd","tid":1627663,"uid":151469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb1f54e0d7a3a8a4196578c5f22eebf28c23e605","tid":1627663,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:01:09.000Z","msg":"去港島,新界九龍人要點走?"},{"pid":"a5fb24ed3888b2de28f85123c5f1a3dac6f731ff","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:01:26.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"a36b7b84541b19819635ccddca785e50b53f4005","tid":1627663,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"九龍港島2區遊行<br />\n唔好推呢個"},{"pid":"b748d1169574b314c2df14527638a409b5406e80","tid":1627663,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"拉 明白心意但遷就下<br />\n<br />\n港九兩區同步啦<br />\n利申港島人"},{"pid":"bdfe1c9625a8bf439ed7e560fc81a351285c204e","tid":1627663,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"師兄知唔知九龍有紅隧去香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cc043bcf8969c4238d5b8f477b40481def27cf","tid":1627663,"uid":165224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdfe1c9625a8bf439ed7e560fc81a351285c204e","tid":1627663,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"師兄知唔知九龍有紅隧去香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:06:08.000Z","msg":"封過啦<br />\n不過如果最後淨係港島搞 <br />\n走唔到我都會照出港島<br />\n <br />\n利申新界人"},{"pid":"9675f3c3389b3bd13d3e95fa89480d94d67ea614","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"宜家所有文宣都係老地方<br />\n你地突然殺出黎話九龍區 會唔會太急<br />\n我認同係好多人易走<br />\n但會唔會係聽日搞？<br />\n<br />\n你個遊行係好 留返下星期搞 大把人會跟你去<br />\n仲有大把時間做文宣<br />\n點9解 要炒大車 兩條戰線去做？"},{"pid":"70a51033017cf8cc9935dc36089988d6c838b09a","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"d3cd26510ec0f929621d9808fec2824d1ce26cad","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:07:44.000Z","msg":"12點先黎分散人頭<br />\n一句封黨鐵就出唔到<br />\n咁成世比黨鐵撚 唔洗再吹大雞啦"},{"pid":"126f669c35b46e1a387a98c66471349650c7dbca","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"對手就係最驚呢樣野<br />\n一直唔批比民陣<br />\n今日一班和理非身體力行出哂去宣傳<br />\n你地一句走唔到就分散"},{"pid":"5439265d1e13906de3a52c3183776dac25878cbf","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e97dad5a13911601a7e6df81e6bdc6013969868","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de1064ed4a6d39968d1927d3b2aa6b98f6323310","tid":1627663,"uid":226991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"屌 成班自毁長城"},{"pid":"fe56d8571c86c4b559d7ec4b5cf2a642b5c32c18","tid":1627663,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b748d1169574b314c2df14527638a409b5406e80","tid":1627663,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"拉 明白心意但遷就下<br />\n<br />\n港九兩區同步啦<br />\n利申港島人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"你話拉又唔用不推文，想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef8e5a0d1f935bbc4b3ad024d7428c474e1b5fc","tid":1627663,"uid":63511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:38:59.000Z","msg":"咁冇連登嗰啲叔叔姨姨點知？<br />\n成日見到佢地去連儂牆影日程表，<br />\n或者開花嗰陣問我地日程<br />\n<br />\n我地今日無啦啦吹死城風已經賣完佢地一次<br />\n好彩今日冇打佢地啫<br />\n<br />\n要分區唔係唔得，唔係咁撚突發凌晨改囉<br />\n好似10.1一早講明會好啲<br />\n<br />\n一係就星期五晚開花嗰陣講，<br />\n好多叔叔問星期六日點<br />\n<br />\n中年人同銀髮需要我地保護㗎"},{"pid":"cf1fd81f83fdc036470ccb2b18e22fb554b17e2b","tid":1627663,"uid":63511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:03:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}